      },
      {
        "Language": "ENG",
        "Name": "The Graceful Apex Rathian",
        "Client": "Ditzy Hunter",
        "Description": "I TOTALLY thought that Rathian\r\nwas \u0027bout done for, \u0027cause it looked\r\nlike, SUPER beat up. But then it\r\ngot mad, and it was, like, soooo\r\nSTRONG! Like, what even is its\r\nproblem, y\u0027know? Anyway, can\r\nyou hunt it for me? Thaaanks!",
        "Target": "Hunt an Apex Rathian",
        "Fail": "Reward hits 0, or time expires"
      },
      {
        "Language": "FRE",
        "Name": "Gracieuse Rathian sup\u00E9rieure",
        "Client": "Chasseur paum\u00E9",
        "Description": "Je pensais que la Rathian\r\n\u00E9tait cuite, elle avait\r\nl\u0027air mal en point... Et puis\r\nelle s\u0027est \u00E9nerv\u00E9e d\u0027un coup,\r\net elle \u00E9tait super forte !\r\nJ\u0027ai rien compris ! Bref,\r\ntu pourrais t\u0027en occuper ?",
        "Target": "Chasser une Rathian sup\u00E9rieure",
        "Fail": "Prime \u00E0 0 ou temps expir\u00E9"
      },
      {
        "Language": "ITA",
        "Name": "La Rathian Apex aggraziata",
        "Client": "Cacciatore sbadato",
        "Description": "Ero convintissimo che quella\r\nRathian fosse ferita, sembrava\r\nproprio stremata. Ma poi si \u00E8\r\ninfuriata ed \u00E8 diventata cos\u00EC\r\nfooorte! Che diamine ha che\r\nnon va? Comunque, potresti\r\ncacciarla per me? Graaazie!",
        "Target": "Caccia una Rathian Apex",
        "Fail": "Premio a zero o tempo scaduto"
      },
      {
        "Language": "GER",
        "Name": "Die anmutige Apex-Rathian",
        "Client": "Alberner J\u00E4ger",
        "Description": "Ich war SICHER, die Rathian\r\nwar am Ende, so wie die aus-\r\ngesehen hat, aber dann wurde\r\nsie RICHTIG w\u00FCtend und sooooo\r\nSTARK! Was hat die eigentlich\r\nf\u00FCr ein Problem? Egal, jagst du\r\nsie bitte f\u00FCr mich? Daaanke!",
        "Target": "Erjage eine Apex-Rathian.",
        "Fail": "Belohnung auf 0 oder Zeit\r\nl\u00E4uft ab."
      },
      {
        "Language": "SPA",
        "Name": "La gr\u00E1cil Rathian Apex",
        "Client": "Cazador despistado",
        "Description": "Estaba convencid\u00EDsimo de que\r\naquella Rathian estaba herida\r\nporque estaba hecha un birria.\r\nPero se volvi\u00F3 loca, \u00A1y menuda\r\nfuerza! \u00BFA qu\u00E9 vino tant\u00EDsima\r\nviolencia gratuita? En fin,\r\n\u00BFy si la cazas por m\u00ED?",
        "Target": "Caza una Rathian Apex",
        "Fail": "La recompensa cae a 0\r\no se acaba el tiempo"
      },
      {
        "Language": "RUS",
        "Name": "\u0413\u0440\u0430\u0446\u0438\u043E\u0437\u043D\u0430\u044F \u0432\u044B\u0441\u0448\u0430\u044F \u0420\u0430\u0442\u0438\u0430\u043D\u0430",
